                            <!--Title-->
                            <h3 class="card-title mt-2 pb-4">
                                <strong>How It Works?</strong>
                            </h3>
                            <!--Text-->
                            <p class="card-text" style="font-size:15px;">LifeWork is the on-demand freelance work
                                service that provides a seamless customer experience whilst liberating the freelance
                                workforce. The freelance economy is dominated by marketplaces that exploit freelancers
                                and leave customers wasting hours of their own time in return for poor quality output.
                                With flexible work becoming the dominant means of task completion, there is desperate
                                need for a new model.
                                We believe that LifeWork is the answer.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text" style="font-size:15px;">LifeWork is an intermediary between customers
                                and freelancers that actively rectifies the problems that occur on marketplaces when
                                the two parties are forced to interact directly with one another.</p>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <!--/.Card-->
                </div>
