                        <!--Card content-->
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <!--Title-->
                            <h4 class="card-title">
                                <strong>Why not to use a marketplace?</strong>
                            </h4>
                            <!--Text-->
                            <p class="card-text">To understand the genius of LifeWork you need to understand the myriad
                                problems of freelance marketplaces. Customers
                                waste hours posting a job and screening the hundreds of freelancers that apply before
                                frequently selecting the cheapest
                                one because they often don't know any better. Management of the project absorbs much
                                more time than initially expected
                                due to miscommunication and a knowledge gap between the freelancer and the customer.
                                The final output is often poor
                                quality, requiring the customer to pay to get it improved or spend time rectifying it
                                themselves.</p>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <!--/.Card-->
                </div>
                <!--First columnn-->

                <!--Second columnn-->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <!--Card-->
                    <div class="card mb-r wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.4s">

                        <!--Card image-->
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="./../img2.jpg" alt="Card image cap">

                        <!--Card content-->
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <!--Title-->
                            <h4 class="card-title">
                                <strong>For the customer</strong>
                            </h4>
                            <!--Text-->
                            <p class="card-text">LifeWork requires minimal input from our customers to get digital
                                freelance work done. A one hour consultation with an
                                expert LifeWork project manager is all that's needed to fully understand your project,
                                and you will receive a quote for
                                the work within 24 hours. LifeWork will select the best person for the job and manage
                                the work from start to finish. If
                                the work needs no check-in milestones then you can go back to your day job and your
                                output will arrive by the deadline,
                                otherwise short check-in video meetings will be held so you can have your input on the
                                ongoing work.LifeWork quality guarantee - if the output doesn't
                                meet the requirements then we'll
                                rework it so that it does.</p>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <!--/.Card-->

                </div>
                <!--Second columnn-->

                <!--Third columnn-->
