                    <!--Card-->
                    <div class="card wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.6s">

                        <!--Card image-->
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="./../img1.png" alt="Card image cap">

                        <!--Card content-->
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <!--Title-->
                            <h4 class="card-title">
                                <strong>For the freelancer</strong>
                            </h4>
                            <!--Text-->
                            <p class="card-text">LifeWork aims to be the best place to work. Period.

                                Freelancers join the network and are informed of the flow of work coming into the
                                platform to know what work to expect.
                                Freelancers will receive work requests that they can be confident meet their
                                preferences - they would have been
                                selected by an expert project manager with AI assistance. The freelancer then works
                                within the structure of templates
                                and milestones set out by the PM but still with a large degree of freedom. The project
                                managers are responsible for
                                ensuring quality meaning that LifeWork guarantees payment to the freelancer even if the
                                customer is unhappy with the
                                final deliverable. Feedback between the PM and freelancer ensure that both people
                                continue to grow.</p>
                        </div>

                    </div>
